pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-20_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-edERGn cHFtyQ pf-21_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-23_">Our Brand &amp; Production Ethics</span></h2><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-24_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-26_">As a brand and a manufacturer we are able to ensure that our brand ethics also apply on our production.</span></p><div data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion" class="sc-cNKqjZ diijrs pf-27_"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-28_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-29_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="dcc92925-10d1-4a57-a648-d6b44ef4fbb6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Safe Work Environment</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="dcc92925-10d1-4a57-a648-d6b44ef4fbb6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-31_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-32_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-33_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-34_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-36_">Our production studio in Lima, Peru is a safe work environment, keeping our workers protected from physical and mental harm. We make sure that in our studio there is:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-dcgwPl kGdrcc pf-37_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-38_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-40_">No Child Labor</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-41_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-43_">No Unpaid Labor</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-44_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-46_">No Discrimination</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-47_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-49_">No Gender Inequality</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-50_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-52_">No Health Threats</span></li></ul><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-53_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-55_">Our founders actively participate in all stages of our work and are present daily in our production studio, looking for ways to improve and working hand in hand with our workers.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-56_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-57_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e1576e59-7da9-4cbc-83bc-7a3320ea626c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Wages</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e1576e59-7da9-4cbc-83bc-7a3320ea626c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-59_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-60_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-61_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-62_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-64_">We provide our workers with waves that are above the minimum wage standard in Peru. We aim to reward them with more benefits as soon as we become profitable.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-65_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-66_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="bc7a3320-ea62-4c62-930e-56377dd27869" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Gender Equality & Empowerment</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="bc7a3320-ea62-4c62-930e-56377dd27869" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-68_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-69_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-70_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-71_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-73_">At AYA, we accept workers of all genders. Our company consists of our founders, marketing team, art team, assistants, accountants and production workers. As of May 2022, we have 36 employees and freelancers working with us, 27 of whom are women.</span></p><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-74_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-76_">Everyone at AYA can use their voice freely to disclose their opinions and ideas. They have a high level of autonomy in their day-to-day activities.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-77_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-78_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="7dd27869-2fb9-479c-bc8d-444cbe51ea65" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Racial Justice</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7dd27869-2fb9-479c-bc8d-444cbe51ea65" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-80_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-81_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-82_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-83_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-85_">AYA is an inclusive brand which is why nobody is discriminated for their nationality or color. Our team is formed of people of different ethnicities, who contribute to the company's development with their unique knowledge and perspective. Our employees and freelancers are from the United States, Latin America and Europe.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-86_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-hJZKUC ifpKHf pf-87_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/studioworker-1656962192536_1200x.jpg?v=1656962195" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/studioworker-1656962192536.jpg?v=1656962195 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9fb8" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-gHjyzD fopdnV pf-88_ pf-bg-lazy"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-JEhMO dxozkW"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-89_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-90_ pf-bg-lazy pf-hide"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-91_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-edERGn cHFtyQ pf-92_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-94_">Our Goals</span></h2><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-95_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-97_">We made sure that from the start everything on our end is done legally and without causing any harm. But that is not where it ends for us. We aim to:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-dcgwPl kGdrcc pf-98_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-99_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-101_"><b>Provide our people with more than living wages.</b><br>As soon as we become a profitable brand, we will upgrade our reward and benefit system to ensure all of our workers our happy in their work life, as well as in their private life.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-ehIJor kvifwM pf-102_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-104_"><b>Become inclusive to every-body.</b><br>We plan to add more sizes, gender neutral clothes, and one size fits all items so that everyone can buy sustainable clothes.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f9ac" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-gHjyzD fopdnV pf-105_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-JEhMO dxozkW"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-106_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-107_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-edERGn cHFtyQ pf-108_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-110_">Our Suppliers</span></h2><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-111_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-113_">We plan to share information about our fabric and components suppliers as soon as we position ourselves on the market. At this moment, sharing everything about us could compromise the future of our business, but we give you our word that we use ethical practises in all stages of our production.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-114_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-116_">We take responsibility for our impact across the whole product lifecycle: impact on the environment, people and animals. We make sure that each part of our supply chain, from raw materials to product disposal, have zero to minimal impact on the environment and living beings.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-cbb3" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-gHjyzD fopdnV pf-117_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-JEhMO dxozkW"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-118_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-119_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-hJZKUC ifpKHf pf-120_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/alpacas-1656962477528_1200x.jpeg?v=1656962480" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/alpacas-1656962477528.jpeg?v=1656962480 1536w" width="3000" height="2000" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fydGpi bMfPUC pf-121_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-edERGn cHFtyQ pf-122_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-124_">Animal Rights</span></h2><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-125_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-127_">We do not use any fur, leather, down/feathers, angora, and exotic animal skins.</span></p><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-128_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-130_">The only material of animal origin, that we plan to incorporate into our catalog in 2022 or 2023, is Royal Alpaca Wool, sourced from small Peruvian co-op farmers. All alpacas are non-mulesed, receive regular medical care, and roam free in the highlands in the Andes Mountains.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>
